title: (VIDEO) Tennessee football as a DirecTV commercial
text:
(VIDEO) Tennessee football as a DirecTV commercial FOX Sports 
Oct 2, 2015 at 1:40a ET + 
Can Butch ditch his cable in the fourth quarter? Randy Sartin / USA TODAY Sports FOX Sports Updated Oct 2, 2015 at 1:40a ET 
Tennessee will enter the Arkansas game with a split record of 2-2, the same results the team has had every season under Butch Jones. The fact the Vols are so painfully close to a 4-0 record make this season's record hurt much more than the others. 
Vol fans can't help but feel their team is split into two categories: first half Tennessee and second half Tennessee. In case you were fortunate enough to miss the first four games of the Tennessee season, this video does a marvelous job of explaining what you may have missed and the roller coaster of emotions currently being experienced by Big Orange Nation: true 
Well done sir, well done. MORE NEWS: Want stories delivered to you? Sign up for our College Football newsletters.
